title: Villa Saxe Eiffel hotel
description:
A pleasant small hotel.  In 1998 the breakfast was very good, and the location is quiet, but not to far from the Metro.  The view up the Avenue de Saxe towards the Eiffel Tower is spectacular at night.  The only draw back is the lack of many restuarants in easy walking distance.

http://www.villa-saxe-eiffel.com/en/home-paris-hotel

title: Statue de la Liberté
description:
Modèle original en bronze de la Statue de la Liberté offert par Bartholdi au musée en 1900, puis installé dans le jardin en 1906.
